Subject: remoteproc: qcom_q6v5_wcss: add IPQ9574 support

Add the IPQ9574 WCSS data and reset/start/stop sequence used by the
native Q6 firmware loader. This lets the IPQ9574 q6v5_wcss node bind as a
remoteproc provider for the integrated ath11k AHB device.

Also load the optional M3 firmware image used by IPQ9574 firmware
packages and point the IPQ9574 firmware names at OpenWrt's ath11k
firmware installation path.

Signed-off-by: Alexandru Gagniuc <mr.nuke.me@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Igor Kravchenko <igor.kravchenko05@gmail.com>
